      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "Documents Needed to Complete Our Review",
        "message": "=<!doctype html>\n<html>\n    <head>\n        <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n        <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\" />\n        <title>Documents Needed to Complete OUR Review</title>\n        <style>\n            @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {\n                .container {\n                    width: 100% !important;\n                }\n                .stack {\n                    display: block !important;\n                    width: 100% !important;\n                }\n                .pad {\n                    padding-left: 16px !important;\n                    padding-right: 16px !important;\n                }\n            }\n            img {\n                border: 0;\n                -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;\n                display: block;\n            }\n            a {\n                color: inherit;\n                text-decoration: none;\n            }\n        </style>\n    </head>\n    <body\n        style=\"\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n        \"\n    >\n        <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" role=\"presentation\">\n            <tr>\n                <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding: 20px 10px\">\n                    <table\n                        class=\"container\"\n                        cellpadding=\"0\"\n                        cellspacing=\"0\"\n                        border=\"0\"\n                        width=\"600\"\n                        role=\"presentation\"\n                        style=\"\n                            width: 600px;\n                            max-width: 600px;\n                            background-color: #ffffff;\n                            border-radius: 6px;\n                            overflow: hidden;\n                        \"\n                    >\n                        <tr>\n                    \t\t<td style=\"padding:30px;background-color: #00314D;\">\n                    \t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0; width: 100%;text-align: center; color: #fff; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;\"><b><span style=\"color:#E03431;\">QUICK & EASY APPROVALS.</span> STRAIGHTFORWARD PROCESS.</b></p>\n                    \t\t</td>\n                    \t</tr>\n                        <tr>\n                            <td style=\"padding: 30px; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff\">\n                                <img\n                                    src=\"http://canadianmerchantcashadvance.ca/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/logo-cmca.png\"\n                                    alt=\"CMCA Finance\"\n                                    width=\"160\"\n                                    style=\"display: block; border: 0; outline: none; text-decoration: none; margin: auto;\"\n                                />\n                            </td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                            <td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding: 10px 45px; color: #515967;\">\n                                <p style=\"margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px; color: #15243C;\">Hello,</p>\n                                <p style=\"margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px; color: #15243C;\">\n                                    Your CMCA application has been securely received through DocuSign and is now moving to the next stage of review.\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"margin: 0 0 30px 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; color: #515967;\">\n                                    To continue with your financing request, please take a few minutes to finalize your application online:\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; text-align: center; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px; color: #00314D;\">\n                                    COMPLETE YOUR APPLICATION\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"margin: 0 0 30px 0; text-align: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px; color: #C5221F;\">\n                                    Final Step\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"margin: 0 0 30px 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 22px; color: #515967;\">\n                                    <b>To complete our underwriting review, we require your business bank statements for the previous 2–3 months.</b> Once we receive your statements, our underwriting team will finalize the assessment and prepare the financing options available to you.\n                                </p>\n\n\n                                <p style=\"display: block; max-width: 460px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto 30px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400px; line-height: 19px; text-align: center; color: #515967;\">\n                                    <i>If you'd like to discuss next steps or have questions, you may also schedule a call with us. Please let us know the best phone number to reach you and a convenient time for a brief call. We're here to make this process clear, secure, and efficient: <a href=\"mailto:underwriting@cmcafinance.com\">underwriting@cmcafinance.com</a>.</i>\n                                </p>\n                                <div style=\"display: block; max-width: 460px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; height: 1px; background-color: #E1E6EF;\"></div>\n                            </td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                            <td>\n                                <p style=\"display: block; max-width: 510px; margin: 30px auto; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: #C5221F;\">CMCA is committed to responsible, secure, and transparent lending.</p>\n                                <table\n                                    width=\"460\"\n                                    cellpadding=\"0\"\n                                    cellspacing=\"0\"\n                                    border=\"0\"\n                                    role=\"presentation\"\n                                    style=\"margin: 0 auto;\"\n                                >\n                                    <tr>\n                                        <td>\n                                            <p style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: #15243C;\">We are accredited by the Better Business Bureau</p>\n                                            <p style=\"margin:0; display: block; text-align: center;\">\n                                                <img src=\"http://canadianmerchantcashadvance.ca/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/logo-bbb.png\" width=\"150\" style=\"display: inline-block;\" />\n                                            </p>\n                                        </td>\n                                        <td>\n                                            <p style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: #15243C;\">Proud member of the Canadian Lender Association</p>\n                                            <p style=\"margin:0; display: block; text-align: center;\">\n                                                <img src=\"http://canadianmerchantcashadvance.ca/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/logo-cla.png\" width=\"150\" style=\"display: inline-block;\" />\n                                            </p>\n                                        </td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    <tr>\n                                        <td colspan=\"2\">\n                                            <p style=\"margin: 30px auto; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 19px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #15243C;\">Note: If you prefer to complete a PDF version of the application instead, simply reply to this email to request the form. Docusign is the preferred method.</p>\n                                            <div style=\"display: block; max-width: 460px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; height: 1px; background-color: #E1E6EF;\"></div>\n                                        </td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                </table>\n                            </td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                            <td>\n                                <table\n                                    width=\"460\"\n                                    cellpadding=\"0\"\n                                    cellspacing=\"0\"\n                                    border=\"0\"\n                                    role=\"presentation\"\n                                    style=\"margin: 0 auto;\"\n                                >\n                                    <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 17px; color: #515967; margin-top:30px;\"><b>CMCA – Canadian Merchant Cash Advance</b><br/>Underwriting & Client Services</p>\n                                    <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 17px; color: #515967;margin-bottom:30px;\"><b>CMCA Finance® Corporate Office</b><br/>309 Lakeshore Blvd. Pointe-Claire, QC H9S 4L6<br/>Phone: <a href=\"tel:18556512844\">1-855-651-2844</a><br/>Fax: <a href=\"tel:18555416893\">1-855-541-6893</a><br/><a href=\"www.canadianmerchantcashadvance.ca\" target=\"_blank\">www.canadianmerchantcashadvance.ca</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:underwriting@cmcafinance.com\" target=\"_blank\">underwriting@cmcafinance.com</a></p>\n                                </table>\n                            </td>\n                        </tr>\n                    </table>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n    </body>\n</html>\n",
